HEADWORD: Womanliness
<hw>Wom"an*li*ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or
state of being womanly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There is nothing wherein their <qex>womanliness</qex> is more
honestly garnished than with silence.</q> <rj><qau>Udall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

